title: Polygon Guild Ahmedabad
Description: Hello Developers, Techies and fellow Web3 enthusiasts Thank you so much for joining us this Sunday [24th April,2022] for the first ever in-person Meetup at Polygon Guild Ahmedabad and making it a success. As promised, we are here to deliver your one-of-kind NFT. Additionally, if you've not a part of our Meetup group yet, do join in with the link below to stay updated on our future events and do help us spread the word.
